Package: keen-pbr
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCHITECTURE@
Maintainer: Maxim Kurbatov <maxim+keen-pbr@kurb.me>
Depends: @DEPENDS@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Homepage: https://github.com/maksimkurb/keen-pbr
Description: Policy-based routing daemon with REST API and Web UI
 keen-pbr routes traffic selectively by IPs, CIDRs, and domains.
 This package includes the daemon, REST API, dnsmasq integration helper,
 and bundled frontend assets.
